        <hr/>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Michael Hoffman was born on November 30, 1956 in Hawaii, USA. He is a director and writer, known for <a href="/title/tt0117247?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">One Fine Day</a> (1996), <a href="/title/tt0140379?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">A Midsummer Night's Dream</a> (1999) and <a href="/title/tt0824758?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">The Last Station</a> (2009). He is married to Samantha Silva.            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0001355/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
   
  <time datetime="1956-11-30" itemprop="birthDate">
<a href="/search/name?birth_monthday=11-30&refine=birth_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_bth_monthday"
>November 30</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?birth_year=1956&ref_=nm_ov_bth_year"
>1956</a>    
  </time>
            in
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=Hawaii,+USA&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>Hawaii, USA</a>
    </div>

                        
                        
                   </td>
